Be able to suspend and wait for an event to complete (GPU compute, etc.), 1 suspend maximum / Job
Can check "am I already done" before scheduling the actual Job
Can redirect to an singleton instance if the actual Job is already running
Can send a signal to notify other Jobs when finished.
